languages.text: "Если вы вскоре не проявите милость, шерин... Что ж. Придется мне по старинке справляться со своими проблемами. В одиночку".
"If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."
languages.original_text: "Если вы вскоре не проявите милость, шерин... Что ж. Придется мне по старинке справляться со своими проблемами. В одиночку".

languages.text: « Si vous ne m'accordez pas votre faveur sans tarder, shereen... eh bien, je n'aurai plus qu'à régler mes problèmes à l'ancienne. Seule. »
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."

languages.text: "Wenn Ihr mir nicht bald Eure Gunst gewährt, Shereen, tja ... Dann muss ich meine Probleme eben auf altbewährte Art und Weise lösen. Allein."
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."

languages.text: “如果你不能快点帮我这个忙的话，亲爱的……恐怕我只能用我的老办法解决问题了，我自己一个人办。”
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."

traits.locale_text: “如果你不能快点帮我这个忙的话，亲爱的……恐怕我只能用我的老办法解决问题了，我自己一个人办。”

languages.text: «Si no me concede su favor pronto, shereen... tendré que resolver mis problemas a la antigua. Por mi cuenta».
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."

traits.locale_text: «Si no me concede su favor pronto, shereen... tendré que resolver mis problemas a la antigua. Por mi cuenta».

languages.text: 「シャリーン、すぐに応えてもらえないのであれば…昔ながらの方法で問題を解決するしかないわ。独りでね」
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."

traits.locale_text: 「シャリーン、すぐに応えてもらえないのであれば…昔ながらの方法で問題を解決するしかないわ。独りでね」

languages.text: "Şirinim, bana bir iyiliği çok görürsen yakında... Başka yollara başvurmak zorunda kalacağım. Kendi yollarıma."
languages.original_text: "If you do not grace me with your favour soon, shereen, well... I will just have to solve my problems the old-fashioned way. On my own."
